<emphasis id="B970EAFEFFF8F6168CB23E45F9B9F5E1" bold="true" box="[1452,1564,2649,2682]" pageId="60" pageNumber="118">Habitat.</emphasis>
Mid-montane forests at elevations of 
<quantity id="4CFC9B09FFF8F616812E3E45F76FF5E1" box="[2096,2250,2649,2682]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" metricValueMax="9.0" metricValueMin="7.0" pageId="60" pageNumber="118" unit="m" value="800.0" valueMax="900.0" valueMin="700.0">700-900 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
